Trails,by,is,a,hybrid,bookmarking,platform,that,allows,for,the,collection,of,curated,bookmarking,lists,called,trails,but,with,an,additional,social,Q,A,component,Users,can,post,questions,and,other,users,can,post,answers,in,the,form,of,bookmark,trails,It,hopes,to,offer,a,new,way,to,combat,information,overload,by,combining,the,functionality,of,social,bookmarking,sites,with,those,of,Q,A,sites,The,Trails,by,API,allows,users,to,search,existing,trails,and,requests,by,page,rating,topic,or,new,status,It,also,allows,search,by,keyword,Calls,are,returned,in,JSON,format